    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737340/extras/03_多种角色，不同体验.PNG?t=1737527172\" /></span>六边形战士小侠客、手搓火球的小师妹、精通召唤的机关师，再到村门口的大黄和误入凡间的二师叔......多种身份多种开局，每一个都是新体验。更多角色等你解锁！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737340/extras/7d1f41529097f0abc26bde1c6d1936b2.poster.avif?t=1737527172\" width=600 height=145 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737340/extras/7d1f41529097f0abc26bde1c6d1936b2.webm?t=1737527172\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737340/extras/8e4a9df9d8e78efa9197cfcf3f9d5e04.avif?t=1737527172\" width=620 height=80 /></span>精心制作的立体纸片让游戏可爱又有趣，平凡小角色独步通神；满屏的火球与黑洞，特效越帅打人越狠。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737340/extras/199683c05932d9028f1d17d5294a7f92.poster.avif?t=1737527172\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737340/extras/199683c05932d9028f1d17d5294a7f92.webm?t=1737527172\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737340/extras/199683c05932d9028f1d17d5294a7f92.mp4?t=1737527172\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737340/extras/05_两两组合，强力神通.PNG?t=1737527172\" /></span>获得特定的技能能够组成更为强大的组合技，发挥1+1＞2的能力，至于有哪些强力的组合，去探索吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >今天你发现了几个组合技呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737340/extras/920d51627dbbb940591c5ef85ac22a5c.poster.avif?t=1737527172\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737340/extras/920d51627dbbb940591c5ef85ac22a5c.webm?t=1737527172\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737340/extras/异兽降临，武装代打.PNG?t=1737527172\" /></span>谁说肉鸽战斗只有刷刷刷？兔兔、鸭鸭……奇趣异兽有百般本领，更能武装进化，治疗压制两不误。召唤异兽，令你爱不释手！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737340/extras/f6e3aa537875d85788f55e8fde34c802.poster.avif?t=1737527172\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737340/extras/f6e3aa537875d85788f55e8fde34c802.webm?t=1737527172\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737340/extras/f6e3aa537875d85788f55e8fde34c802.mp4?t=1737527172\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737340/extras/07_元宝重铸，逆天改命.PNG?t=1737527172\" /></span>每一次升级都是一次破局的提升机会。金元宝更能重铸技能，氪金改命。更有局外天赋养成，助力你的下一场桃林之约。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737340/extras/e1f91dbd1c1489c843802350461ccda8.poster.avif?t=1737527172\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737340/extras/e1f91dbd1c1489c843802350461ccda8.webm?t=1737527172\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737340/extras/e1f91dbd1c1489c843802350461ccda8.mp4?t=1737527172\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎各位逃友加入官方讨论群：626548639 或 619696673，畅聊桃源秘籍。</p>",
